    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase Statutory Paternity Leave to 3 months",
        "additional_details": "I think it is unfair that mothers are entitled to up to a year leave, but fathers are only entitled to two weeks. Fathers should be given more time to spend time with and bond with their children.",
        "background": "I'd like the Government to increase Statutory Paternity Leave to 3 months, to give dads better opportunities to spend time with their new children.",
